{"type":"text","timestamp":1775879470995,"sessionID":"ses_28558a73bffe63pzmnHs6VtxMQ","part":{"id":"prt_d7aaa3639001c5jEE9iumj0TnC","messageID":"msg_d7aaa24d0001iwGuO3ad79WYEV","sessionID":"ses_28558a73bffe63pzmnHs6VtxMQ","type":"text","text":"I've updated the delta-spec.md file to focus on AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端. The spec now covers the HTTP底层客户端 implementation including:\n\n- **ControlPlaneClient**: Workload Manager control plane with session creation/deletion, auth token handling, environment variable resolution\n- **CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient**: Router data plane for code interpreter with base URL construction, session headers, file operations, command execution with timeout buffer\n- **AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient**: Router data plane for agent runtime with session bootstrapping, invoke POST requests\n- **HTTP utilities**: `create_session` with connection pooling, `read_token_from_file`, `get_logger`\n\nAll requirements use GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios in OpenSpec format.","time":{"start":1775879470992,"end":1775879470992}}}
